      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SLICK NITRO (1) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (38.43) at Bendigo in a Restricted WIN. Has first look at box 1 this time. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can find winning form. PAW FORTRESS (4) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at The Meadows in a handy 30.25 beating Inspection. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Expected to feature again. EDWARD NIGMA (8) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from five tries. Placed last time (34.96) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 2.5 lengths. Can feature with the right run. IRISH ZOE (7) cannot be ruled out.",
